{
  "texts": [
    "compared orthopedic residents' performance with ChatGPT-3.5 and GPT-4 on 180 orthopedic assessment questions from 9 orthopedic subspecialties.",
    "Residents scored 74.2%, GPT-4 scored 47.2%, and ChatGPT-3.5 scored 29.4%, with residents significantly outperforming both AI models.",
    "GPT-4 outperformed ChatGPT-3.5.",
    "Both AIs did better on text-based questions than image-based ones, with ChatGPT-3.5 scoring 37.8% vs. 22.4% (text vs. image based) and GPT-4 scoring 61.0% vs. 35.7%.",
    "Resident performance did not significantly differ between image-based and text-only questions."
  ]
}